overview.en: Libra is a computing coin issued by Weitao capital. It is a distributed asset interaction network supported by distributed bitcoin mine computing power. Libra directly anchors BTC computing power and enjoys the BTC daily dividend mechanism of holding money is mining for a long time.
overview.zh: LIBRA是伟涛资本发行的算力币，是以分布式比特币矿场算力为底层资产支撑的分布式资产交互网络。LIBRA直接锚定BTC算力，长期享“持币即挖矿”的BTC每日分红机制。
